Package: STAT297iMDBProject
Type: Package
Title: Movie Determination Utility
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Darragh Caruso, Tara Peng, Dylan Shoemaker, Aaron Wilhelm
Maintainer: Aaron Wilhelm <aaronwilhelm15@gmail.com>
Description: A tool designed to determine a suitable movie for a user.
    The user may filter through different options to choose a movie.
    Once a movie is chosen, it can be clicked on and the user is then directed
    to the movie's iMBd page. 
